        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-inner">
                <div class="card-front">
                    <img src="./assets/5.jpg" alt="Yoga">
                </div>
                <div class="card-back">
                    <h3>Yoga</h3>
                    <p>Find balance between mind and body with our yoga programs suitable for all experience levels.</p>
